items.title: Duckburg Wiki
items.headline: Venture down the boulevard of adventure!
items.desc:
The Duckburg Wiki delves into the comic book universe created by ninth art legend Carl Barks and further developed by Don Rosa. 

From everyday craziness and gags to an epic saga that spans over eight decades and globetrotting ducks discovering mythical artifacts, every fiber of this universe is testimony to the reason that it contains some of the most unique characters in popular culture.
